<p><a href="https://photos.smugmug.com/photos/i-zQz33Gt/0/O/i-zQz33Gt.jpg"><img class="center" src="https://photos.smugmug.com/photos/i-zQz33Gt/0/X2/i-zQz33Gt-X2.jpg"></a></p>

<p><strong>えいごで:</strong> <em>Kichijoji</em> is the number one place where people in Japan wish to live. This charming neighbourhood has many small shops and borders on <em>Inokashira</em> park.</p>

